<p class="ayah 30-11" id="11" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَبْدَؤُاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">originates</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْخَلْقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the creation,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُعِيدُهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He repeats it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُرْجَعُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will be returned.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>11<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
